name: Neon Icon Guitar series
description: The NFT Neon Icon Guitar was inspired by a copy of a historic photo in the 1969, it was worked on free software using neon as a way to highlight the evident colors. The buyer will have, in addition to the NFT, a file in the 1900 x 2729 pixel png format. This is the first in a series to be released. Buy this one to help me launch the next one.
